{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775844615381,"sessionID":"ses_2876da30fffem0jOE59UJnZgLJ","part":{"id":"prt_d78926aae0015mVWxNm0pXPLwc","messageID":"msg_d78925de50013US10yiRsSKFtc","sessionID":"ses_2876da30fffem0jOE59UJnZgLJ","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_aec673a056e4463b842f4e27","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure (top-level directories and key files)\n2. The pkg/picod module - what exists there already, all files and their purposes\n3. Any existing middleware patterns in the project (look for middleware, auth, JWT patterns anywhere)\n4. Any existing task.md or tasks.md files to understand the format used\n5. Any design documents related to ST-3 or AR-017\n6. The go.mod file to understand dependencies\n7. Any existing JWT-related code or configuration\n8. How authentication/authorization is currently handled (if at all)\n9. Any existing test patterns in the project\n\nReturn ALL findings in detail - file paths, contents summaries, and any relevant code snippets. Be very thorough.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2876d7fb1ffeHKE0Y81ctCQWaY (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the entire project. Here is the complete detailed report:\n\n---\n\n## AGENTCUBE PROJECT -- COMPREHENSIVE EXPLORATION REPORT\n\n### 1. OVERALL PROJECT STRUCTURE\n\n**Root directory:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z`\n\n**Top-level directories and key files:**\n\n| Entry | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| `.sdd_prompt.md` | file | SDD prompt configuration |\n| `changes/` | dir | Change requests (AR-001 through AR-017), each with proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md, and optionally delta-spec.md |\n| `ci-cd/` | dir | CI/CD configuration |\n| `cli-toolkit/